		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<div class="package_info">
				<img src="https://www.visitthecatskills.com/sites/default/files/styles/600x300_footer_promotion/public/demo-footer-packages-promo-collage.jpg?itok=z8gzEKcH">
