			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-5">
				<div class="company_info">
					<img src="/static/images/logo.png">
					<p>All content, photography, programming Â© High Country Life for Tourism Services, 2018.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-3 col-sm-offset-1">
